name: Siaki Tuikabe
story: Siaki Tuikabe was born in the Caribbean and grew up with a deep appreciation for law and order. He joined the military to serve his country and make a difference in his community. After several years of service, he transitioned to the police force, where he has since become a respected member of the team. Siaki is known for his courage and determination, often diving headfirst into dangerous situations to protect his fellow officers and civilians.
